Join us for "Improving Accessibility in Computing Courses: Open Office Hours" on December 18, 2025, at 10:00 AM PST. This event is designed for educators, students, and anyone interested in enhancing accessibility in computing education. Attendees can expect to engage in discussions, share ideas, and seek guidance on best practices for making computing courses more inclusive. Whether you have specific questions or just want to learn more about accessibility strategies, this open forum provides a supportive environment to explore solutions. Don't miss this opportunity to contribute to a more accessible learning experience for all.
